OL,3,CLightning strikes homes setting them
OL,4,Con fire
OL,6,FFire crews across East and West Sussex
OL,7,Fhave dealt with a series of lightning
OL,8,Fstrikes, some of which have set houses
OL,9,Fon fire.
OL,11,FLightning is reported to have started
OL,12,Ffires in Crawley, Bexhill and
OL,13,FEastbourne.
OL,15,FEast Sussex Fire and Rescue Service
OL,16,Fwas called during the early hours of
OL,17,Fthe morning on 27 June 2026 to a roof
OL,18,Falight on a house in Selmeston Road,
OL,19,FEastbourne.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/4
