OL,3,CLightning strikes homes setting them
OL,4,Con fire
OL,6,FThey were called to Long Avenue in
OL,7,FBexhill following reports a house was
OL,8,Falight after being struck by lightning.
OL,10,FJoint Fire Control have received
OL,11,Fmultiple 999 calls.
OL,13,FCrews from East Sussex Fire and Rescue
OL,14,FServuce and West Sussex Fire and
OL,15,FRescue Service worked hard to bring
OL,16,Fthe fires under control.
OL,18,FFour fire engines sent to each
OL,19,Fincident.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/4
