OL,3,CLightning strikes homes setting them
OL,4,Con fire
OL,6,FAll properties affected have suffered
OL,7,Fserious damage.
OL,9,FThere are no reports of injuries.
OL,11,FA spokesperson for East Sussex Fire
OL,12,Fand Rescue Service said: "Joint Fire
OL,13,FControl received sixteen 999 calls
OL,14,Fabout the Bexhill incident and five
OL,15,Fabout the Eastbourne incident during
OL,16,Fwhat has been a very busy night for
OL,17,Fstaff."
