OL,3,CLightning strikes homes setting them
OL,4,Con fire
OL,6,FKent Fire and Rescue Service was
OL,7,Fcalled to reports of a house fire on
OL,8,FUplees Road in Faversham after
OL,9,Flightning struck the roof.
OL,11,FLightning also hit the loft space of a
OL,12,Fhouse on Newton Road in Faversham.
OL,14,FCrews were also called to reports of a
OL,15,Fhouse fire on Ulcombe Hill in Ulcombe,
OL,16,FMaidstone after lightning struck the
OL,17,Froof.
OL,19,FThere were no reported injuries.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/4
